title: BONUS Ep. #5 | Eric vs. Food Temptations
description:
Welcome back to the show! Here’s another update on Eric’s shenanigans from his quarantine home in L.A. Apparently he’s been living his best life during isolation… except for all the food temptations. Can anyone relate?
Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
